quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'ii on jeddu…óo aayeeje amen …óe, o wi'i: "Maatun mi okkee jawdi e …ìi…ó…óo"."
  19,78,"Enee o ∆¥elliti e ko wirnii kon, kaa jogiti ka jurmotoo…óo e Aadi?"
  19,79,"Wonaa non, aray Min mbinnda ko o wi'ata kon min …ìeydana mo immorde e Lepte …óen …ìeydude."
  19,80,"Min ndonna mo e ko o wi'ata ko, o ara e Amen ko o weddii…óo(gooto)."
  19,81,"∆Åe njogitii ga Alla dewetee…ói fii yo …ói laatano …ìe semmbe."
  19,82,"Wonaa non, ma…ìe njeddu dewugol…ìe ngol, …ìe laatanoo …ìe a√±…ìe."
  19,83,"Enee a yiaani minen min Nulii Seytanuuji e dow yeddu…ìe …ìen hi…ói ∆¥uuna …ìe ∆¥uunudee."
  19,84,"Wata a hawjan …ìe, pellat, limonay…ìebe kala limugol."
  19,85,"√ëande Min moo…ìoyta huloo…ìe [Alla] …ìe ka jurmotoo…óo Teddinaa…ìe."
  19,86,"Men cogga bon…ìe …ìe haa ka Jahannama ko …ìe joloo…ìe."
  19,87,"∆Åe maraa tefoore nden si wonaa on jogitii…óo ka jurmotoo…óo Aadi."
  19,88,"∆Åe mbi'i: "jurmotoo…óo jogitike …ìi…ó…óo"."
  19,89,"Goo≈ã…óii on mgaddii hu'unde pankar…óii nde."
  19,90,"Kammuuli …óin no do'a(…óesa) se'ekaade immorde e …óuum leydi ndin feera pelle …óe nduuya fii unagol."
  19,91,"fii …ìe noddanii jurmotoo…óo …ìi…ó…óo."
  19,92,"Haananaa jurmotoo…óo de o jogitotoo …ìi…ó…óo."
  19,93,"Alaa ko woni e kammuuli e leydi si wanaa o aray e jurmotoo…óo hombo woni jeyaa…óo."
  19,94,"Goo…óii o moftii …ìe o limii …ìe kadi e limugol."
  19,95,"[Gooto] Kala e ma…ì…ìe aray Mo √ëande Darngako o woddii…óo(teeld…óo)."